snippet.title: Need for Speed: Carbon Collector's Edition Gameplay Challenge Series - Challenge Bronze [PS2]
snippet.description:
Title: Need for Speed: Carbon Collector's Edition Gameplay Challenge Series - Challenge Bronze [PS2]

About: About: Need for Speed: Carbon, also known as NFS Carbon, is an Electronic Arts video game in the Need for Speed series and is also the sequel to Need for Speed Most Wanted. Released in 2006, it is the tenth installment, preceded by Need for Speed: Most Wanted.

NFSTV is a dedicated fan-channel keeping you up to date with all the latest news, video walkthroughs and official trailers of the most successful video game racing franchise Need for Speed, published by Electronic Arts.
